---
---

<section class="bg-myna-black relative overflow-hidden">

  <!-- Large decorative quote mark -->
  <div class="absolute top-8 left-6 lg:left-16 text-[18rem] font-bold leading-none text-myna-amber/05 select-none pointer-events-none font-serif">
    "
  </div>

  <!-- Amber diagonal accent bar -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-myna-amber opacity-60"></div>

  <!-- Bottom decorative pattern -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 pointer-events-none opacity-5"
    style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #F5A623 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 20px 20px;">
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">

      <!-- Pull quote -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-10">
          <span class="h-px w-8 bg-myna-amber"></span>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber">
            The belief
          </span>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-bold text-myna-white leading-snug tracking-tight">
          "The elders must create the stage. The young must show up with spirit
          and put in the work. The cost is borne by the elders —
          <span class="text-myna-amber">but the young must pay too.</span>
          They pay with effort."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: body copy -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-myna-brown/40 pt-8 lg:pt-0 pl-0 lg:pl-12 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-myna-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          India has an education system that produces graduates — but not
          builders. We teach content. We don't teach how to learn, how to
          fail, how to think, or how to show up.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-myna-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          EduMyna exists to close that gap. Not by replacing the system,
          but by building what the system doesn't — the meta-skills, the
          stage, the community, the tools.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/story"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber hover:text-myna-white transition-colors">
          Read the full story →
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
